WEBVTT

00:04:28.333 --> 00:04:31.809
and stop putting everything on God.

00:04:31.833 --> 00:04:34.059
God has given us everything we need.

00:04:34.083 --> 00:04:36.643
It's right here, let's use it.

00:04:36.667 --> 00:04:39.768
But here's the thing,
my favorite part of what I do

00:04:39.792 --> 00:04:42.809
is featuring Africans doing amazing work,

00:04:42.833 --> 00:04:45.059
ordinary people touching lives.

00:04:45.083 --> 00:04:47.726
Like this Kenyan woman, Wangari Maathai,

00:04:47.750 --> 00:04:51.559
the first African woman
to receive the Nobel Peace prize,

00:04:51.583 --> 00:04:53.351
for standing up for human rights

00:04:53.375 --> 00:04:55.518
and planting a million trees.

00:04:55.542 --> 00:04:57.684
Also this Zimbabwean woman,

00:04:57.708 --> 00:04:59.101
Dr. Tererai Trent,

00:04:59.125 --> 00:05:02.476
who was married off at the age of 14